cs.NI, cs.DC, cs.SY, cs.IT, cs.PF 

Reasoning: 
- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is the most likely category as the paper deals with wireless sensor networks and time synchronization. 
- cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) is also likely as the paper discusses multi-hop communication and the use of gateways. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a possibility as the paper deals with clock frequency and time estimation. 
- cs.IT (Information Theory) is a possibility as the paper discusses timestamp values and their translation. 
- cs.PF (Performance) is a possibility as the paper analyzes the impact of adding a gateway on the performance of the time synchronization scheme.
